462
00:31:56,979 --> 00:31:59,504
你是你家族血脉的最后一人了
安德莉亚
You are the last one
of your bloodline, Andrea.

463
00:32:01,350 --> 00:32:04,615
或是海莉，不管你怎么称呼自己
Or Hayley.
Whatever you call yourself.

464
00:32:06,922 --> 00:32:09,254
这些人会跟随你
These people will follow you.

465
00:32:09,425 --> 00:32:12,519
你可以帮助他们
你以及你所代表的
You can help them,
you and what you represent.

466
00:32:12,694 --> 00:32:14,685
那到底是什么呢？
And what is that exactly?

467
00:32:14,863 --> 00:32:19,766
一切还是不同的时候
我们的族人还在抗争的时候
A time when things were different,
when our people fought back.

468
00:32:21,437 --> 00:32:24,167
你历经艰辛找到我们
And after everything
you went through to find us.

469
00:32:26,175 --> 00:32:27,938
你是唯一能打破诅咒的人
You're the one
who's gonna break our curse.

470
00:32:29,545 --> 00:32:31,775
你在说什么？
What are you talking about?

471
00:32:33,449 --> 00:32:35,041
你的女巫朋友
Your witch friend.

472
00:32:35,217 --> 00:32:36,912
她告诉伊芙她今晚会来
She told Eve
she was coming here tonight

473
00:32:37,085 --> 00:32:38,177
解除我们的咒语
to set us free.

474
00:32:39,254 --> 00:32:41,654
等等，什么女巫朋友？
Wait. What witch friend?

475
00:32:52,835 --> 00:32:54,393
抱歉
I'm sorry.

476
00:32:54,570 --> 00:32:57,869
我真的很喜欢你
但我跟别人约定好了
I really do like you
but this is the deal we made.

477
00:32:58,040 --> 00:33:01,942
什么约定？跟谁？
What deal? With whom?

478
00:33:51,727 --> 00:33:52,989
海莉
Hayley.

479
00:33:53,161 --> 00:33:55,595
以利亚，女巫们在谋划着什么
Elijah, something's going on
with the witches.

480
00:33:55,764 --> 00:33:59,825
听我说，你说得没错
莎莉丝特回来了
Listen to me. You were right.
Celeste is back.

481
00:34:00,002 --> 00:34:03,096
尼克劳斯、蕾贝卡
你们的处境都很危险
Niklaus, Rebekah.
You're all in danger.

482
00:34:05,340 --> 00:34:06,807
- 怎么回事？
- 这是个陷阱
-What's going on?
-It's a trap.

483
00:34:06,975 --> 00:34:08,943
- 我没跟任何女巫做过约定
- 什么？
-I didn't make a deal with witches.
-What?

484
00:34:09,111 --> 00:34:10,806
海莉，你得找到蕾贝卡
Hayley, you have to find Rebekah.

485
00:34:10,979 --> 00:34:12,503
在我到之前和她待在一起
And you stay with her
until I get there.

486
00:34:15,250 --> 00:34:17,810
以利亚，这是个咒语
我们被困在屋内了
Elijah, it's a spell.
They're trapping us inside.

487
00:34:39,408 --> 00:34:41,842
你知道怎么做
You know what to do.

488
00:34:48,183 --> 00:34:49,775
我们得离开这里
We have to get out of here.

489
00:35:03,532 --> 00:35:04,965
来，透过这个呼吸
Here. Breathe through this.

490
00:35:24,353 --> 00:35:27,516
- 蕾贝卡呢？
- 不知道
-Where's Rebekah?
-I don't know.

491
00:35:29,391 --> 00:35:30,449
她跟其中一个人出去了
She went off with one of them.

492
00:35:30,626 --> 00:35:33,686
以利亚，我朋友还在里面
Elijah, my friend is still in there.

493
00:35:53,415 --> 00:35:54,939
站起来
On your feet.

494
00:36:06,128 --> 00:36:07,117
帮帮我
Help me.

495
00:36:07,295 --> 00:36:09,729
好久不见了，蕾贝卡
It's been such a long time, Rebekah.

496
00:36:12,334 --> 00:36:15,792
我会好好享受这过程的
I'm going to enjoy this.

497
00:36:29,284 --> 00:36:30,876
丢了什么东西吗？
SABlNE: Missing something?

498
00:36:33,622 --> 00:36:35,715
你不会伤害我的
我是唯一活着
You won't hurt me.
I'm the only one alive

499
00:36:35,891 --> 00:36:37,984
能打破海莉家族诅咒的人
who can break the curse
on Hayley's family.

500
00:36:38,160 --> 00:36:40,560
而洁妮薇知道你妹妹在哪
And Genevieve knows
where your sister is.

501
00:36:42,364 --> 00:36:45,561
贝丝蒂娜把克劳斯
藏在一个安全的地方
Bastiana has Klaus
tucked away someplace safe.

502
00:36:45,734 --> 00:36:47,895
顺便说一句，他正在痛苦煎熬
He's suffering horribly,
I might add,

503
00:36:48,070 --> 00:36:50,561
那都是因为你选择去救那只小狼
and all because you chose
to save the little wolf

504
00:36:50,739 --> 00:36:51,728
而不是你的家人
instead of your own blood.

505
00:36:56,812 --> 00:36:58,279
多么可怕的结局
What a horrific ending...

506
00:37:02,117 --> 00:37:04,415
对你那可悲病态的家族来说
...to your pathetic, diseased family.

507
00:37:13,095 --> 00:37:16,496
我想“永远”终究不会是永恒
I guess "always" isn't forever after all.

508
00:37:20,569 --> 00:37:22,400
我得走了，月亮
I have to go. The moon.

509
00:37:22,571 --> 00:37:23,902
听着，杰克森
Listen, Jackson,

510
00:37:24,072 --> 00:37:27,940
我想谢谢你保护我
不只是今晚
I want to thank you
for protecting me, not just tonight.

511
00:37:28,110 --> 00:37:29,907
我从儿时起就一直幻想着
I've been dreaming
about meeting you,

512
00:37:30,078 --> 00:37:31,067
我们的见面
since I was a kid.

513
00:37:33,148 --> 00:37:35,616
我从没想过会变成这样
I never thought it would go like this.

514
00:37:36,818 --> 00:37:38,649
嘿
Hey...

515
00:37:40,689 --> 00:37:43,021
我会一直寻找
直到找到打破诅咒的方法
...I won't stop until I find a way
to break this curse.

516
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:46,689
我保证
I promise.

517
00:37:52,868 --> 00:37:55,962
快点，快点，快点接啊
Come on. Come on. Come on.

518
00:37:57,439 --> 00:37:59,464
克劳斯，你在哪？
Klaus, where are you?

519
00:37:59,641 --> 00:38:03,771
米卡森先生现在正身体不适
Mr. Mikaelson is currently indisposed.

520
00:38:04,846 --> 00:38:06,541
怎么了？你做了什么？
What happened?
What did you do?

521
00:38:06,715 --> 00:38:11,015
什么都没做
有人替你完成了你的任务
I did nothing.
Someone completed your task for you.

522
00:38:11,186 --> 00:38:13,347
如果你得到了你想要的，那我叔叔…
If you got what you wanted,
then my uncle--

523
00:38:13,522 --> 00:38:15,956
很快就会死去，并且会极其痛苦
Will die soon and in great anguish.

524
00:38:17,459 --> 00:38:19,859
你瞧，亲爱的
你没能遵守我们的协定
You see, dear, you failed
to hold up your end of our bargain.

525
00:38:20,028 --> 00:38:22,588
你叔叔多次与邪恶为友
You chose instead to side with evil

526
00:38:22,764 --> 00:38:25,130
而你也和他一样
as your uncle has done
many times before you.

527
00:38:26,535 --> 00:38:27,524
不过振作点
But take heart.

528
00:38:27,702 --> 00:38:29,499
他的惩罚将会弥补
His punishment will atone

529
00:38:29,671 --> 00:38:31,502
他数次尝试阻止收获祭
for his attempts
to prevent the Harvest.

530
00:38:31,673 --> 00:38:33,937
他的痛苦将会净化他
His suffering will purify him.

531
00:38:34,109 --> 00:38:35,838
你吸取他的教训就会做得更好了，孩子
You'd do well
to heed his lesson, girl.

532
00:38:36,011 --> 00:38:39,640
与我们作对就是与自然秩序作对
To oppose us
is to oppose the natural order.

533
00:38:39,815 --> 00:38:43,012
无论自愿或被迫
By choice or by force,

534
00:38:43,185 --> 00:38:47,053
法语区的女巫们将再次崛起
the witches of the French Quarter
will rise again.

535
00:38:52,761 --> 00:38:54,353
我们到处都找过了
We looked everywhere for him.

536
00:38:54,529 --> 00:38:56,497
把女巫区、墓地都翻遍了
Tore apart the Cauldron,
the City of the Dead.

537
00:38:56,665 --> 00:38:58,724
不管他被抓到哪，一定不在法语区
Wherever they got him,
he ain't in the Quarter.

538
00:38:59,901 --> 00:39:00,890
马赛尔！
ELlJAH: Marcel!

539
00:39:01,069 --> 00:39:03,401
我弟弟在哪？
Where is my brother?

540
00:39:03,572 --> 00:39:06,268
我的人正在外面找他
I got guys out looking for him
right now.

541
00:39:11,446 --> 00:39:12,640
以利亚
Elijah.

542
00:39:14,683 --> 00:39:16,708
克劳斯又冲我发脾气了
Klaus threw one
of his classic temper tantrums,

543
00:39:16,885 --> 00:39:19,877
扭断了我的脖子
试图独自一人与一群女巫较量
snapped my neck, tried to take
on a coven of witches by himself.

544
00:39:20,055 --> 00:39:21,215
结果被制服了
He got dropped.

545
00:39:21,389 --> 00:39:23,482
我不知道他在哪，也不知道怎么找他
I don't know where he is
or how to find him.

546
00:39:23,658 --> 00:39:26,525
她们还抓走了蕾贝卡
They also have Rebekah.

547
00:39:30,565 --> 00:39:35,400
在场的每一人都要帮我找到他们
Every one of you will help me
to find them!

548
00:39:38,406 --> 00:39:40,499
我要把她们都杀光
I'm going to kill them all.

549
00:39:46,081 --> 00:39:49,744
- 快点，我们该走了
- 我不想走
-Come on. We have to go.
-I don't wanna go.

550
00:39:51,052 --> 00:39:53,418
莫妮克，这没得商量
Monique, this isn't a debate.

551
00:39:53,588 --> 00:39:55,385
我刚刚捅了一个真祖
I just stabbed an Original.

552
00:39:55,557 --> 00:39:57,821
他一旦恢复就会杀了我的
He's gonna kill me
as soon as he's recovered.

553
00:39:59,661 --> 00:40:04,064
听着
对于这一切我很抱歉
Look, I'm sorry for everything.

554
00:40:04,232 --> 00:40:07,793
我应该在那个愚蠢的收获祭前
把你救出来的
I should have come and got you
before that stupid Harvest.

555
00:40:09,571 --> 00:40:11,664
但你还是可以拥有正常的生活
But you can still have a normal life.

556
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:17,972
没有这些疯狂荒诞的女巫事
One without all this crazy witch nonsense.

557
00:40:20,081 --> 00:40:21,776
但我就是女巫
But I am a witch.

558
00:40:23,785 --> 00:40:26,049
我不想走
And I don't want to go.

559
00:40:30,158 --> 00:40:31,557
莫妮克？
Monique?

560
00:40:33,061 --> 00:40:36,724
祖先们说你的信念不坚定
The ancestors said
you didn't have enough faith.

561
00:40:36,898 --> 00:40:38,661
我还希望是他们错了
I was hoping they were wrong.

562
00:40:39,734 --> 00:40:40,962
我早该知道的
I should have known better.

563
00:40:46,341 --> 00:40:49,367
- 莫妮克
- 你试图阻止收获祭
-Monique.
-You tried to stop the Harvest.

564
00:40:49,544 --> 00:40:50,738
求你不要这么做
Please don't do this.

565
00:40:50,912 --> 00:40:53,403
现在我们该留下来战斗时，你却想逃走
Now you want to run
when we need to stay and fight.

566
00:40:53,581 --> 00:40:55,606
别这样，求求你，不要，不要
Please. I'm begging you, don't--
Don't--

567
00:40:55,784 --> 00:40:57,183
我们四个人，我们死而后生时
The four of us, when we return,

568
00:40:57,352 --> 00:41:00,014
就有足够的力量除掉城里的吸血鬼
we'll have enough power
to rid the city of vampires

569
00:41:00,188 --> 00:41:01,450
我们会杀死每一个
and we'll kill anyone...

570
00:41:03,892 --> 00:41:05,450
信念不坚定的人
...who doesn't keep the faith.

571
00:41:09,497 --> 00:41:12,660
- 莫妮克，求求你
- 你应该相信的
-Monique, please.
-You should have believed.

572
00:41:12,834 --> 00:41:15,701
住手，求求你
Stop. Please.

573
00:41:49,471 --> 00:41:55,000
片名：创始吸血鬼（第一季）

